A Second Response
-----------------
Is someone going to answer Mr. Silvers' question on the logic of import
embargo re _Aedes albopictus_? Perhaps the embargo logic entails a worry
that the foreign-born mosquitos are carrying a "foreign" disease. We are
all still wondering just "how" West Nile virus entered the USA.
--
Patricia A. Doyle, PhD
<dr_p_doyle@hotmail.com>
